"Time-Traveling Bunny's Adventures": A children's book series that follows the adventures of a time-traveling bunny as it travels through different eras and periods, encountering historical figures and events. The bunny uses its time-traveling powers to learn about history and make new friends.

"The Time-Traveling Bunny's Cookbook": A cookbook that features recipes from different eras and periods, as discovered by the time-traveling bunny. Each recipe includes a brief history of the dish and the time period it comes from.

"The Time-Traveling Bunny's Time Machine": A virtual reality game that allows players to explore different eras and periods through the eyes of the time-traveling bunny. Players can interact with historical figures and events, and even make changes to the timeline.

"The Time-Traveling Bunny's Time Traveling Tour": A guided tour that takes visitors on a journey through different eras and periods, as seen through the eyes of the time-traveling bunny. The tour includes visits to historical sites, encounters with famous figures, and even a chance to try traditional dishes from different time periods.

"The Time-Traveling Bunny's Time-Traveling Journal": A journal that chronicles the time-traveling bunny's adventures as it travels through different eras and periods. The journal includes sketches, notes, and even recipes from different time periods, as discovered by the bunny.
